'''維珍可樂'''（{{lang-en|'''Virgin Cola'''}}），是由[[維珍集團|維珍集團]]和維珍飲料於1994年推出的一種[[碳酸|碳酸]][[可樂|可樂]]飲料。維珍可樂在市場上的主要競爭對手為可口可樂、百事可樂。<ref name=independent161094>{{cite news|last=Hosking|first=Patrick|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4681573.html|title=Virgin deputy shuns new cola|newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=16 October 1994|accessdate=27 November 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513033835/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4681573.html|archivedate=2013年5月13日}} {{subscription required}}</ref>

==歷史==
維珍可樂在1990年代初期與科特飲料合作。科特飲料在此之前一直在尋找具有吸引力的國際品牌。

1994年，維珍可樂於與英國超市零售商[[樂購|樂購]]達成了[[分銷協議|分銷協議]]。<ref name=independent161094/>

1996年，維珍可樂在[[英國|英國]]，[[法國|法國]]，[[比利時|比利時]]和[[南非|南非]]等地相繼推出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A553187 |title=h2g2 - Cola Drinks |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2010-11-02}}</ref><ref name=wp260398>{{cite news|last=Mayer|first=Caroline E.|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-639280.html|title=Branson Throws The Cola Biz a Curve; Virgin's CEO Plans U.S. Launch for `Pammy'|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=26 March 1998|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513023905/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-639280.html|archive-date=2013-05-13|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

1998年，[[理查德·布蘭森|理查德·布蘭森]]親自出席了維珍可樂在美國上市的宣傳活動，最為注目的是布蘭森開著一輛[[T-54/55系列主战坦克|T-54/55]]坦克進入紐約市的[[時報廣場|紐約時代廣場]]。維珍可樂隨後與美國零售商，包括[[塔吉特百貨公司|塔吉特百貨公司]]達成了分銷協議。<ref name=pt130598>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-10848FA54412E772.html|title=VIRGIN COLA TAKES AIM AT COCA-COLA'S SOFT DRINK STRANGLEHOLD|newspaper=Post-Tribune|date=13 May 1998|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513035233/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1N1-10848FA54412E772.html|archive-date=2013-05-13|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required }}</ref><ref name=wt290898>{{cite news|last=Fisher|first=Eric|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-56762413.html|title=Virgin Cola faces uphill fight: Britain's new No. 3 gears for area push.(Business)|newspaper=The Washington Times|date=29 August 1998|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610081635/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-56762413.html|archive-date=2014-06-10|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

2001年4月，維珍飲料退出美國，維珍可樂當時在美國市場只剩下0.5％的份額，比起其在1998年的份額（14.5%）減少逾9成。<ref name=mw270701>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-78358297.html|title=Will global markets embrace Virgin?|newspaper=Marketing Week|date=27 July 2001|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513111839/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-78358297.html|archive-date=2013-05-13|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

2002年，[[維珍雲呢拿可樂|維珍雲呢拿可樂]]在英國推出，比起競爭對手可口可樂更早推出類似的產品。<ref name=mw121202>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-96134992.html|title=Virgin Cola trumps Coca-Cola with first UK launch of vanilla variant. (News).(Virgin Cola to introduce Virgin Vanilla soft drink in United Kingdom)(Brief Article)|newspaper=[[Marketing_Week|Marketing Week]]|date=12 December 2002|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513023919/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-96134992.html|archive-date=2013-05-13|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

2004年，維珍飲料宣佈停止供應維珍雲呢拿可樂，以集中推廣青少年市場。<ref name=mw180304>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-114819845.html|title=Virgin Cola relaunch to target teen market.(News)(Brief Article)|newspaper=Marketing Week|date=18 March 2004|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513020345/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-114819845.html|archive-date=2013-05-13|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

==銷售==

維珍可樂曾於英國，法國，比利時和南非等地出售。維珍集團旗下的[[維珍航空|維珍航空]]在其大西洋航班上也會供應維珍可樂。<ref name=wp260398>{{cite news|last=Mayer|first=Caroline E.|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-639280.html|title=Branson Throws The Cola Biz a Curve; Virgin's CEO Plans U.S. Launch for `Pammy'|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=26 March 1998|accessdate=27 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513023905/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-639280.html|archive-date=2013-05-13|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

1998年，維珍可樂在美國擁有14.5%的[[軟性飲料|軟性飲料]]市場佔有率，僅低於百事可樂的30.9%和可口可樂的43.9%，成為當時全美第三大可樂飲料供應商。維珍可樂曾表示其銷售策略是基於不同年齡的人的意見和看法。<ref>[http://articles.latimes.com/1998/may/13/business/fi-49128 Virgin Cola: Is U.S. Ready? - Los Angeles Times May 13, 1998]</ref>

